{"tid":1175830,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母","createTime":"2019-05-28T22:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T16:11:45.000Z","uid":238801,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"07f7cc69494cefd7b990ccdfc00123ea57df6278","tid":1175830,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T22:03:50.000Z","msg":"連續周到2隻甲由喺我廁所坑渠爬入嚟<br />\n激撚死我<br />\n仲要2次都係急尿想痾嗰陣嚟見到<br />\n一大一細屌你老母買一送一咩<br />\n我點撚樣沖涼呀 一陣沖沖下又爬一隻入嚟我真係死比你睇<br />\n爬撚夠入嚟未姐屌你老母<br />\n啲甲由真係垃圾嚟 屌"},{"pid":"bda586a8bdec9130ef545d3aceaa8a2a32b0aa9e","tid":1175830,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T22:05:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母你爬入嚟我又嚇親你又要死 都唔明你爬入嚟做乜柒<br />\n噴撚到成枝清潔劑冇撚曬<br />\n仲要我想講我從來唔煮食 屋企真係屎都冇得食<br />\n你地咁都要爬入嚟 食屎<br />\n屌 好撚嬲屌你老母呀！！"},{"pid":"1b0c2a1c54d011148ad3de8b44fd4e1d3f849263","tid":1175830,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T22:06:59.000Z","msg":"嚇到我兩次都痾唔撚到尿 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩我冇瞓覺姐 有瞓你地咪搬撚曬入嚟開p?<br />\n屌我好撚驚之前都係有只係我周唔到 但我屋企真係屎都冇得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔得好驚 聽日要人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5a5b6c3707ab2338afa2259107c2516d27883e","tid":1175830,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T22:07:32.000Z","msg":"雖然我長開冷氣姐 唔代表開嚟比你地涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食屎啦"},{"pid":"1e517aee93274e3ee7cfd57d4ecd73614c6bdc9f","tid":1175830,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T22:29:29.000Z","msg":"想貼曱甴圖 有冇人阻止我<img src=\"/a